social_posts.post_text: We’re engaged!! 💍🥹😆❤️‍🔥 Chris proposed in late March of 2022 and it kicked off one of the most eventful years of our lives together. Excited to finally share the beautiful news here!! Thank you to TJ, Sam, Lexi & Bryan for helping to make this day so special.♥️♥️♥️
✨Thank you, 2022. For the family, travel, celebrations, & love. Never could have imagined how eventful and unifying this year would be.

🌸 I haven’t posted here in a while so for any new friends… Hi, my name is Alina Brown. I am the founder of @auralignshop, a metaphysical stationary company that produces things like astrology planners, wall calendars, & notebooks. 

I am also a holistic nutritionist & the founder of @wellnesscon, an annual outdoor conference focused on promoting diversity within the wellness space through BIPOC healer-focused workshops, talks, & panels on all things wellness & business building. Things were slowed down (to say the least) thanks to the global pandemic but I’m excited to say that we’re getting back to planning gatherings soon!

Day-to-day, you’ll find me making weekly YouTube videos for my channel that consists of informational wellness, astrological, and seasonal topics centered on aligning with the patterns & wisdom of earth & the cosmos.

And yes, I have Gemini all over my natal chart so I carry many hats and enjoy exploring different mediums that are all tied to helping others live in alignment with the many rhythms and cycles of this world & cosmos!

I believe in the power of preventative medicine through public health advocacy, and the power that fostering healthy communities has. 

Nice to meet ya!
Peace! 🌳🧘🏽‍♀️🌸

🕯️🤍🌿Things that have brought me joy this Spring. Festival & markets w/ my love, finally remembering when the Space Mountain photo is taken instead of being terrified (Chris’ pose is better), fresh mugwort from my neighbor’s backyard, Disneyland randomly selling boba, my surprise 30th birthday party (that deserves its own post because..still processing 🥹), looking at wedding venues, precious friends & our cats growing from planters.🪴

🌈🤍 camaraderie, guidance, vulnerability, acceptance, & LOVE. grateful for my 30th summer. a time of wedding planning, nesting, traveling, rushing, slowing down, supporting, accepting support, & love love love🧚🏾‍♀️🕯️🌕
✨new full video is up diving deeper. wishing everyone an illuminating Pisces blue moon. 🌕💙 #astrology

🤍Exactly a year ago today, we had our engagement party. Forever deeply grateful for the family, friendship and community that enveloped us in support and joy on this day. Little did we know how full circle this gathering would feel one year later… 🥹🤍 (And thank you to the incredible @karicakesphotography for capturing & being a part of this day!)
Get excited 💫 Details on the 2024 Auralign Planner launch are coming soon 😉
